                    <app><lem type="norm">pinakadadiniṅ</lem><rdg wit="#L642">pinaḥkaḍaḍiniṁ</rdg><rdg wit="#L633">pinakaḍiniṁ</rdg></app> mas kabaih, ndah ya teka yvagya rahayu paṅapusan ta irikaṅ maṇik anargha, paṅikәtan ta irikaṅ maṇik 
